Dog Cuties is the best New tab Search page for Dog lovers on Google Chrome. You can see new cute dog photo every time you open a NEW TAB. Our images are obtained and curated from Google’s vast gallery of images.

Dog Cuties makes your search faster and brings the right search results for you.

By clicking 'ADD TO CHROME', you accept and agree to installing the Dog Cuties extension and setting Chrome™ New Tab to that provided by the service  with web search by Microsoft Bing and the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.

All images used in conjunction with the Dog Cuties extension and corresponding website have been sourced via Google Images and other publicly available image resources at no cost via the Creative Commons License.
